column5: Without Al Jazeera, a prominent news outlet known for its extensive coverage of global events, including those in regions like Gaza, we are left with a significant gap in our understanding of unfolding events. Al Jazeera's comprehensive reporting has provided valuable insights into the complex dynamics and ongoing struggles faced by communities in Gaza and beyond. Its absence means that crucial stories, perspectives, and voices may go unheard, hindering our ability to grasp the full picture of events and their implications. The lack of access to Al Jazeera's reporting underscores the importance of diverse and independent media sources in fostering informed discourse and understanding across borders.

column6: Three years ago by: Nael Abu Marwan One of the axioms of military matters is that armies fight as they train, so it is dangerous to make easy assumptions about combat capabilities based on past performance, societies evolve and so does the military culture. In all its wars with the Arabs, Israel was the victor due to Israel's military and technological superiority against Arab forces that had nothing but slogans. Until there was an intellectual change in the military strategy in the revolutionary Palestinian thought and the use of guerrilla warfare, this matter remained limited for many reasons related to the Arab periphery of Israel and the fear of the Israeli reaction, the revolution was burning in Lebanon, the neighboring country of the Israeli entity and that country was the only remaining outlet for the Palestinian resistance until the invasion of Lebanon by Israel in order to eliminate the Palestinian resistance and the blockade of Beirut in 1982 ... and the subsequent exit of the Palestinian resistance and the dispersal of its elements in the parts of the earth and the subsequent intifada inside Palestine - the very important transformation and the appearance of H Israel and the invincible Israeli army failed and stood helpless in eliminating the tunnels with all the combat and technical means it used, especially in its last devastating war on the Gaza Strip in the summer of 2014. Amos Yadlin, former head of the Israeli army's intelligence division, said that Hamas achieved strategic achievements that cannot be underestimated during the Israeli aggression on the Gaza Strip in 2014, and Yadlin advised the entity's leaders not to minimize and underestimate the achievements made by Hamas during the war, adding: \"Hamas fought for 50 days against the most powerful army in the Middle East, closed Ben Gurion Airport, caused residents of the south to flee their homes and set conditions that prolonged the operation. The transfer is over. Today we stand on the threshold of a new war in 2021, with preparations by both sides, Hamas and the resistance on one side and Israel and its army on the other side ... Everyone was preparing for the battle, with the resistance keen to hide its development, I think Hamas will change its strategy in the next war with (Israel). The next battle, if it continues, will move into the occupied territories, especially around the cities of the Gaza envelope. Perhaps this is a very likely change in strategy for the Palestinian resistance in the war - Hamas and the resistance in Gaza can use drones, attacks launched by the resistance's commandos and naval forces. The resistance in Gaza is preparing for war by using all means to have the ability to fight a war that will be costly and terrifying for Israel - the declaration of war and striking Israel by Gaza and the setting of the sixth hour in support of the people of Jerusalem in their uprising to what is happening to the Sheikh Jarrah neighborhood from settler attacks was not the call from Gaza in announcing the time for war did not come out of a vacuum or lack of ability, but rather realizes what will be. After every war with Israel, the resistance draws lessons, learns lessons, and plans for the next confrontation through which it uses new, more advanced combat methods to confront Israel, Hamas and Gaza in the development of the drone project. What the Mossad did in killing the Tunisian scientist Muhammad al-Zawari is a great proof of what it does and what is hidden in the development of this project, no one can predict what exists and is not easy and simple as we have listed the development in all capabilities and means in preparation for war ... Hamas, which started with funny primitive rockets, those rockets have become a threat to all cities of Israel ... For this, the next war has a surprise as the previous wars had a surprise. The resistance in Gaza has worked to draw lessons from its battles with Israel and is also busy working to increase its strength in preparation for the next major battle. The tunnels that were not in the minds of the State of Israel, but they are useless tunnels. Israel did not realize and did not know what Hamas and the resistance had, and this matter cost it a very large price that it did not expect and no one expected, just as no one expected the development of the funny rockets of Hamas, which became a nightmare for Israel very terrifying in the 2014 war.I believe that the next war with Gaza is not easy and will be very costly, in the book The Art of War by Sun Tzu or Sun Tzu, one of Sun Tzu's sayings is to know yourself and know your enemy to achieve a thousand victories in a thousand battles, Israel, as we witnessed in previous battles with Gaza, did not know anything. The transfer is over. Two words that summarize a battle and determine who is the victor. These two words were used by the resistance in Gaza in its previous war with Israel and will be used in its next war.

column6: The issue is the siege of the Palestinians and the siege of the Arab peoples by the Arab paper states and their armies. The Arab peoples should take to the streets after every prayer and demand the opening of the borders unconditionally, otherwise by force, and you will see wonders. Opening the borders is a legitimate, legal, moral and humanitarian necessity. Let the Arab peoples decide the situation. The scholars should declare a general alarm and open the borders for the Arab peoples, even by force, in order to liberate Jerusalem and Palestine from the Zionist occupiers. O Arab peoples, mobilize lightly and heavily, do not faint or grieve, and you are the most superior, God willing, and enter the door against them, and if you enter it, you are the overcomers, God willing.
